==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Contract system
<hw>Con"tract sys"tem</hw>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>The sweating
system.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The system of employing convicts by selling their
labor (to be performed inside the prison) at a fixed price per day to
contractors who are allowed to have agents in the prison to superintend
the work.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Contract tablet</ent>⟦br⟧
